    <p><em type="italic">Numra </em>is a program for practicing numerals. We recommend Numra to all students of Saami: In order to learn a language you must know its numeral system. </p>
    <p xml:lang="nno"></p>
    <p type="title">Options</p>
    <list>
      <p type="listitem" xml:lang="nno">Range: 0-10, 0-20, 0-100 or 0-1000.</p>
      <p type="listitem">Mode: From number to numeral, and from numeral to number.</p>
      <p type="listitem">Ordinal numbers.</p>
      <p type="listitem">Time</p>
      <p type="listitem" xml:lang="sma">Dates</p>
